FAQ

Q. What kinds of puppies are these?
A: These are a rare colored, miniature Schnauzer pups that originated from Germany.

Q: Where are these puppies located?
A: These pups are in a loving home, under the constant care of responsible professionals in Sanford, Florida.

Q: What if something goes wrong and a puppy gets sick?
A: A regular veterinarian is available 24/7 if an occurrence should arise where one would be necessary. They will go through another thorough veterinary check up before going to their forever homes.

Q: What if I'm interested in adding one of these Schnauzer puppies to my family?
A: Please contact Maximilian Schnauzers via the website: http://www.maximilianschnauzers.com/

Q: I NEED MORE SCHNAUZERS! WHAT DO I DO?!
A: Can't get enough SCHNAUZERS? Join the chat on twitter using #schnauzercam, and check out more fun twitter activity @petcollectivetv.
